# {project_name}

A Vita project for energy system analysis.

## Getting Started

1. Open this directory in your AI agent (Amp, Codex, Claude)
2. The agent will read `AGENTS.md` and understand the workflow
3. Ask a question like: "Run the example model and explain what technologies are selected"

## Commands

```bash
# Validate the example model
vedalang validate models/example.veda.yaml --run demo_2025

# Run the example
vita run models/example.veda.yaml --run demo_2025 --out runs/example --json
```

